Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.68,0:00:13.53,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Sachi-senpai… Megumi… Tsuzuri.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.66,0:00:18.52,Kozue,,0,0,0,,What… What should I do here…?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:24.53,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Can’t sleep?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:27.34,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Tsuzuri…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:30.75,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I don’t often see you awake at this hour, either.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:32.37,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Yeah…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:36.45,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Saya came over earlier.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:42.02,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…Actually, Kaho-san came to my dorm room earlier as well.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:43.75,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Oh.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:51.62,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I assume they told us the same thing, then.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.98,0:01:02.00,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Let’s perform as a full group of four! Together at the Nadeshiko Festival!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.98,0:01:05.92,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I… I need some time to think about it.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.54,0:01:16.34,Kozue,,0,0,0,,How did you respond, Tsuzuri?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:17.95,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I didn’t.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:22.93,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Well… I guess I just thanked her.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.42,0:01:28.13,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,They care a lot about the two of us.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:30.13,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I see.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.24,0:01:32.85,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,What about you, Kozu?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:37.97,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I wasn’t sure myself.\NThat’s why I came here.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.94,0:01:47.28,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…I think you should decide.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:49.71,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…Why?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.82,0:01:54.51,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Because being a school idol isn’t something you should be forced into.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.35,0:01:56.18,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…Tsuzuri.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:01:58.26,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I know.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.19,0:02:04.14,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,We promised we wouldn’t stand on stage together again…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:11.93,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,But we never said anything about performing as four, so…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:15.53,Kozue,,0,0,0,,You have a point.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.96,0:02:20.36,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I suppose the rest is up to me, then.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.53,0:02:26.59,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…That song from back then.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.55,0:02:32.38,Kozue,,0,0,0,,If I worked hard to perform that song one more time…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:36.54,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I could stand alongside you again.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:38.64,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Alongside me?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:43.76,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I mean, I’d like it if you always stood alongside me.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:47.56,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,But that song was…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:52.56,Kozue,,0,0,0,,This time… This time, we’ll do it properly.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:54.96,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…O…kay.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:57.28,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Okay.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:02:59.38,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Hm?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.60,0:03:03.37,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,You’re right. \NIt’s different from before.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:06.53,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,So I’m sure this will go better than before.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:09.16,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Right.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:14.93,Kozue,,0,0,0,,We’re different than we were before…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:17.03,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I know that now.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:18.34,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:21.66,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Now we have Saya and Kaho.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:27.40,Kozue,,0,0,0,,And I’d like to respond to their feelings.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:29.73,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:32.45,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,If we do that,\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:38.08,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I’m sure I’ll finally be able to be a school idol with you this time.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:41.37,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I agree. \NLet’s do this.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:01.88,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Let’s try a four-member performance, then!\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:04.19,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Wow…!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:07.39,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,We did it, Kaho-san!\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:08.51,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Yeah!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:12.53,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I have a request to make of you, in that case.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:18.63,Kozue,,0,0,0,,See…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:23.74,Kozue,,0,0,0,,The thing is, there is a particular song I want to perform at this year’s Nadeshiko Festival.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:26.42,Kaho,,0,0,0,,What kind of song is it?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:34.21,Kozue,,0,0,0,,This song is… very difficult.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:40.44,Kozue,,0,0,0,,It’s also the song that Tsuzuri and I performed at the Love Live! qualifiers.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:47.20,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I am ashamed to admit it, but I wasn’t able to perform it at a level where I would feel comfortable performing it with her.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:50.62,Kozue,,0,0,0,,It’s a song we decided to never perform together again.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:52.33,Kozue,,0,0,0,,So…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:55.47,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Then, we’ll just have to give it another try!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:56.89,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:59.59,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I got this! Leave it to me!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:03.83,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I’ll do everything to support you, Kozue-senpai!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:05.30,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Kaho-san…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:08.60,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Let’s do it! \NAre you in, Sayaka-chan!?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:13.04,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Yes. We’ve come this far for our seniors, after all!\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:16.88,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Kaho-san… Murano-san…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:21.38,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Alright. I’ll… do my best.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:23.48,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Thanks.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:30.45,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,If you didn’t suggest performing as a full group…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:34.39,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,We wouldn’t have thought of trying this song again.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:39.08,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Alright! \NLet’s give it our best shot!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:40.78,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Of course!\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.12,0:05:46.41,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,…Oh, Tsuzuri-senpai.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:47.53,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Yeah?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:50.82,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me more about the song? \N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:52.92,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You too, Otomune-senpai…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:56.43,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You said it was a difficult song, so…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:05:58.97,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Yeah…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:01.44,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Alright, let’s start here, then.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:04.45,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Kozu, do you remember how the choreo went?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:08.92,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…Of course.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:13.12,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Kaho-san, Murano-san, please watch this.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:23.51,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Sorta like that.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:26.61,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Wow…!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:30.50,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,It’s very… creative.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:34.63,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I’m not completely sure, but did Tsuzuri-senpai compose it?\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:35.72,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:42.28,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Whoa… It’s a really cool song!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:45.56,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Really? I’m happy to hear it, then.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:47.34,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Last year…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:51.69,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Tsuzuri suddenly presented it to the club one day. \NShe said she thought she might have finished making a song.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:55.34,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,That sounds like something she would do.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.07,0:06:57.44,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,All I could think of then…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:07:03.50,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Was that I wanted to do my best together with Kozu.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:10.06,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I failed to meet your expectations, though.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:15.78,Kozue,,0,0,0,,But that’s why I wanted to try again, one more time.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:19.82,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,The choreography is very extensive, yet there are still so many subtle details…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:25.42,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I can clearly see how this would be very difficult to perform.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:28.95,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Huh? Was what you just did not good enough?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.32,0:07:30.95,Kozue,,0,0,80,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:30.95,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.17,0:07:33.26,Kaho,,0,0,0,,No hesitation at all!?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:36.91,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Is this what you meant by not being in sync?\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:42.09,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You know, I did notice that something felt a little off…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:43.73,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:50.74,Kozue,,0,0,0,,In any case, one of my deepest regrets is that we never managed to perfect our performance of this song.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:56.47,Kozue,,0,0,0,,So…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:07:59.29,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I really want to get it right this time.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:04.02,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Alright, I get it!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.49,0:08:07.55,Kaho,,0,0,0,,So first, we need to work on getting in sync, right?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.65,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Let’s do this, Sayaka-chan!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:11.58,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,R-Right.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:16.45,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You know I can handle anything, but have you come up with something, Kaho-san?\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:19.48,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Yeah!\N Alright, I’ll go first!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:26.45,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Kozue-senpai, Tsuzuri-senpai.\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:30.31,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You said you were having problems getting in sync, right?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:33.34,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes. I mentioned that, but…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:35.39,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:37.10,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Then…\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:40.28,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You should stick together real close until you get it!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:45.79,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,‘Kay.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.02,0:08:50.13,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Is that what you meant…?\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:51.95,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Just like that!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:53.06,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Huh!?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:56.55,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I have two younger sisters, you know!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:09:01.00,Kaho,,0,0,0,,And they’re always together, so they’re real close!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.51,0:09:02.49,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,So…?\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:03.83,Kaho,,0,0,0,,So!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:08.31,Kaho,,0,0,0,,As long as you’re together, you’ll definitely understand each other better….\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:11.75,Kaho,,0,0,0,,And you’ll get closer and closer!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:17.74,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…F-For how long?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:19.50,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Forever!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:21.19,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I… see…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:28.87,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Otomune-senpai, Tsuzuri-senpai can be a real handful, so… good luck.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:33.70,Kozue,,0,0,0,,A-Are we really doing this!?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:37.03,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I can be a real handful, so good luck.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:50.62,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…A-Alright, fine. I said I’d trust those two, so…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:54.65,Kozue,,0,0,0,,If they think we need this, I guess we’ll just have to do it!\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:26.93,Kozue,,0,0,0,,There’s no way this will work.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:29.43,Kaho,,0,0,0,,No way!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:33.59,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,We have to come up with something else as fast as we can!\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:36.66,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you’re right, Sayaka-chan!\NLet’s figure something out!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:41.78,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Did you hate it, Kozu?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:44.53,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I-I didn’t {\i1}hate{\i0} it…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.44,0:10:49.55,Kozue,,0,0,0,,But at the very least, it’s dangerous for us to be that close during practice, so I think we should stop.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:55.25,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I agree with that…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:57.55,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Hm… \N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:11:01.30,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Okay. I’ll allow it, then.\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:03.82,Kozue,,0,0,0,,T-Thank you…?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:08.90,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,And we can’t just ignore our dance lessons. \NThey’re very important.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.47,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,This is hard…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:14.60,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Well, even though physically getting closer wasn’t the best idea…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:16.94,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Wait, it wasn’t!?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:23.22,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I do agree that you need to be emotionally closer to get in sync.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.25,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,How should we do that?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:28.08,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Hm, well…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:35.20,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,This is just a thought, but maybe if you had a conversation with each other and discussed your worries,\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:40.13,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,then you’ll be able to do something you couldn’t before… probably.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:52.07,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Personally, there are a lot of things I haven’t told you about, Tsuzuri-senpai.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:55.61,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Things like what I worry about my figure skating, for example.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:59.08,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Kozu, is something worrying you?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:01.21,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Nothing in particular…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:03.31,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Alright, done.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:06.19,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,That’s not what I meant!\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:07.74,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,…Ahem.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:09.84,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Anyway, um…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.30,0:12:14.09,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I know you’re already working so hard, but there was something I wanted to talk to you two about.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:17.48,Kozue,,0,0,0,,What could it be? \NIs it something for the article?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:20.27,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, that’s already done.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:25.68,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I wanted to have you check on it before the Nadeshiko Festival,\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:29.65,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,but right now, there’s something more important I need you two for.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:32.13,Kaho,,0,0,0,,And that’s this!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:34.23,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,A festival?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:39.03,Kozue,,0,0,0,,It’s nearly summer, so it’s about that time of year when shrines start holding these kinds of events, huh?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:42.53,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Did you want all of us to go together?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:43.88,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,No, actually. \N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:47.81,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,The thing is, I met up with Reika-san this morning.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:51.72,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Oh, Reika-san. Haven’t talked to her in a while.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:58.04,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,It sounded like she needed more part-timers to help her out. So…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:03.84,Kaho,,0,0,0,,We were hoping you’d go help out!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:06.92,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Wait, us…?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:13.42,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Actually, I already said that you two would go over!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:15.97,Kozue,,0,0,0,,You already did…!?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:17.01,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:21.09,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,She even said she was looking forward to it.\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:22.59,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I see…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:24.40,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Um…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:28.69,Kaho,,0,0,0,,We’re sorry that we’re forcing you into this!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:31.68,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…No, it’s fine.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:33.77,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I probably should be thanking you.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:35.21,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:37.51,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Thanks, you two.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:46.75,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Anyway!\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:50.18,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Kozue-senpai, Tsuzuri-senpai, see you later!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:52.52,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Have a nice trip!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:54.52,Kaho,,0,0,0,,
